Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.61,0:07:35.84,Miring,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Kelas sudah berakhir, aku harus pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:42.47,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.55,0:07:47.70,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Anu ... anu ....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:52.15,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Kau masih belum pulang, ya, Nishimura-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:53.58,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Kau baru mau pulang?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.78,0:07:56.88,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Apa yang kau lakukan sampai belum pulang?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.57,0:08:00.30,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,A-Aku ....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:04.78,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Ka-Kamu juga kenapa masih belum pulang, Takada-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.78,0:08:06.18,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Sebenarnya ....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.18,0:08:08.91,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Pak Guru marah padaku tadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.91,0:08:12.27,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Katanya rencana liburanku terlalu main-main.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.27,0:08:15.73,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Aku harus sudah mengumpulkannya lagi besok.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:21.32,Miring,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Rencana apa yang dia tulis?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:27.43,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Payungku sudah rusak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:28.57,Utama,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(650,1)\fnArial\shad0\fs18.667\fay-.05\c&H535558&\3c&HCAD0D8&\b1\pos(390.123,62.787)}Takada
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.97,0:08:30.56,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Aku juga tidak bawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:33.93,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Apa kita bisa bablas lari ke rumah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:36.45,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Takada-kun ....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:38.56,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Aku minta maaf tadi, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:39.90,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:45.29,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Soalnya rencana liburanku tidak terlau banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:48.67,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Kalau kamu berkenan, sih ....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:49.81,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Kamu mau lihat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:51.12,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Iya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.08,0:08:54.43,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Benar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.77,0:08:56.84,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Jadwalmu kosong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:57.92,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Iya, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.79,0:09:00.63,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Syukurlah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.63,0:09:01.42,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.75,0:09:05.94,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Berarti aku bisa sering main denganmu, Nishimura-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.64,0:09:11.77,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Ka-Kamu mengajakku main?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.77,0:09:12.89,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Tentu saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.37,0:09:17.20,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Malah, kita kembarin rencana kita, yuk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:20.74,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Aku sarankan pergi jalan-jalan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:25.10,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Selain itu, ada gunung, main kembang api,\N menangkap serangga ....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.10,0:09:26.70,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Lalu gunung!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.30,0:09:32.86,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Ada banyak kegiatan dan tempat yang ingin dikunjungi saat libur musim panas, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.36,0:09:37.55,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Asalkan bersamamu, di manapun pasti akan menyenangkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.10,0:09:41.12,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,A-Apa kau tidak mau?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,0:09:44.69,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,TI-Tidak, bukan begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.66,0:09:50.03,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Aku juga ingin bermain bersamamu, Takada-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:52.48,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Syukurlah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:55.83,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Baiklah, kutulis dalam lembar rencanamu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.18,0:09:58.39,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Etto ... gunung!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.39,0:10:00.32,Miring,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Dia terobsesi banget sama gunung.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:02.24,Utama,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(475.038,75.2)\fnhey comic\fs18.667\shad0\bord0\c&H565A4E&\b1\frz349.8}Rencana Libur musim Panas Kelas 5-1
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:06.34,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Aduh, aku tidak bisa menulis di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.34,0:10:08.34,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Sudah jelaslah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.53,0:10:11.46,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Hujannya juga tidak reda-reda.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:14.08,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Padahal aku ingin memenuhi rencana liburan ....
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.73,0:10:19.95,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Ah, mungkin perpustakaan sekolah masih buka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:23.55,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Walau jam sekolah sudah lama berakhir?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.55,0:10:26.05,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Be-Benar juga ....
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:27.78,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Nanti kena marah, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:34.26,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Tenang saja, Nishimura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.26,0:10:36.03,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Asalkan kita pulang sebelum malam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:39.29,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Kalau ada guru datang nanti,\Nkita sembunyi di bawah meja!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.29,0:10:41.29,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Di bawah meja?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:46.09,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Rasanya seperti anak nakal, bikin deg-degan, ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.14,0:10:59.15,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Kelihatannya sepi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:04.77,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Baru kali ini aku masuk perpustakaan yang sepi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.77,0:11:06.60,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Takada-kun, diam!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:08.15,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Maaf, maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.37,0:11:17.09,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Kita seperti sedang menjelajah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.09,0:11:18.64,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,I-Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.37,0:11:22.46,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Saking banyaknya kegiatan yang\N ingin dilakukan bikin bingung, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.54,0:11:30.03,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Aku ingin kita bersama-sama\N melakukan hal yang kamu inginkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.03,0:11:34.19,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Sama! Aku juga ingin melakukan\N hal yang kau inginkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:41.67,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Etto ... pertama-tama mencari monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.67,0:11:43.84,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Lalu memotret hantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:46.09,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Sekalian kita membuat markas rahasia!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.44,0:11:49.98,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Kalau nulis itu, nanti dibilang\N rencananya kurang serius, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:51.09,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.45,0:11:53.61,Miring,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.61,0:11:55.83,Miring,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Menyusun rencana bersama-sama ...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.86,0:11:59.71,Miring,Nishimura,0,0,0,,... adalah untuk membuat janji \Nmelakukan kegiatan bersama-sama.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.07,0:12:06.11,Miring,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Rencanaku sekarang sama seperti Takada-kun.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.57,0:12:10.82,Miring,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Ini adalah libur musim panasku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.54,0:12:13.91,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Ayo sekalian kita berkeliling dunia?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.91,0:12:16.29,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Tidak, kurasa mustahil ....
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.72,0:12:37.03,Utama,Kurashiki-sensei,0,0,0,,Astaga ....
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.03,0:12:39.24,Utama,Kurashiki-sensei,0,0,0,,Sekolah sudah lama berakhir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:49.45,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Kita kena marah, ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:50.73,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Maaf, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:53.86,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Gara-gara aku menyarankan pergi ke perpustakaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.30,0:13:00.43,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Kita harus tambahkan "latihan petak umpet" dalam rencana liburan musim panas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:10.17,Kilas,Takada,0,0,0,,Nishimura-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.13,0:13:14.55,Kilas,Takada,0,0,0,,Ayo kita main yang banyak\Nselama libur musim panas!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.08,0:13:29.54,Utama,Principal,0,0,0,,Ah, jadi ....
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.54,0:13:34.42,Utama,Principal,0,0,0,,Tolong kalian jaga kesehatan jangan bermain berlebihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.42,0:13:38.41,Utama,Principal,0,0,0,,Semoga libur musim panas kalian menyenangkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.43,0:13:41.56,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Tidak sabar libur musim panas, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.56,0:13:43.61,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Masih ingat janji pergi ke kolam renang?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.61,0:13:44.42,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:48.42,Miring,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Besok sudah memasuki libur musim panas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:51.11,Utama,Akane's Father,0,0,0,,Akane.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.81,0:13:55.60,Utama,Akane's Father,0,0,0,,Kau cuma mau main ke kolam renang sekolah, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.60,0:13:56.92,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Iya, sih ....
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.17,0:13:59.74,Utama,Akane's Father,0,0,0,,Kenapa tidak memakai baju renang sekolah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.74,0:14:01.86,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Ti-Tidak bisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:04.16,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Baju renang sekolah ....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:07.32,Kilas,Takada,0,0,0,,Hino-kun bilang ....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.83,0:14:12.52,Kilas,Takada,0,0,0,,Anak kelas lima SD sudah terlihat\N norak pakai baju renang sekolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.81,0:14:16.58,Kilas,Takada,0,0,0,,Makanya harus beli yang baru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.03,0:14:21.08,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Aku juga sudah kelas lima.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:24.68,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Aku malu memakai baju renang sekolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:26.34,Utama,Akane's Father,0,0,0,,Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.91,0:14:29.98,Utama,Akane's Father,0,0,0,,Jarang-jarang kau menginginkan sesuatu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.98,0:14:31.34,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:33.82,Utama,Akane's Father,0,0,0,,Bagaimana dengan ini?\NImut, loh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.82,0:14:36.71,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Ja-Jangan yang terlalu mencolok!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.71,0:14:37.94,Utama,Akane's Father,0,0,0,,Bagaimana kalau ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:40.36,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Ya-Yang wajar-wajar saja ....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:41.90,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Yang biasa saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:43.73,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Tidak usah yang imut-imut!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:47.44,Utama,Akane's Father,0,0,0,,Mendingan pakai baju renang sekolah, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:49.05,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Ti-Tidak mau!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.05,0:14:50.75,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Aku terlalu malu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.79,0:14:57.86,Utama,Akane's Father,0,0,0,,Masa-masa puber yang sulit, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.71,0:15:19.76,Utama,Akane's Father,0,0,0,,Akane, kau sudah memilih?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.76,0:15:21.48,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Se-Sebentar lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:48.08,Miring,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Sama sekali tidak ada yang memakai baju renang sekolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.92,0:15:52.66,Miring,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Untung aku sudah beli baju renang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.66,0:15:58.22,Miring,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Aku malu pakai baju renang sekolah,\Npakai baju renang yang imut pun bakal diejek.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:16:02.19,Miring,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Aku bingung milihnya karena dijuluki Malaikat Maut.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:05.07,Miring,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Bagaimana menurut Takada-kun, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.05,0:16:08.49,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Ah, ketemu juga, Nishimura-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.36,0:16:12.28,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Ta-Ta-Takada-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:13.96,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Aku sudah mencarimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.96,0:16:15.84,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Ayo pergi, Nishimura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:17.71,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Tunggu sebentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.22,0:16:25.27,Miring,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Ba-Baju renangku tidak terlihat aneh, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.57,0:16:40.73,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:42.59,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Ke-Kenapa melongo dulu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.59,0:16:43.97,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Apa aneh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.82,0:16:46.92,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Tenang saja, Nishimura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.31,0:16:49.09,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Ayo buruan pergi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:50.44,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,I-Iya ....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:55.26,Miring,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Mungkin aku salah pilih.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.09,0:17:01.43,Miring,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Mungkin mereka mengira Malaikat Maut\N terlalu sok-sokan ....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,0:17:05.53,Miring,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Seharusnya aku pilih baju renang\N yang lebih biasa lagi ....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.84,0:17:09.39,Utama,Kitagawa,0,0,0,,Hei, lihat itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.45,0:17:13.76,Utama,Kitagawa,0,0,0,,Malaikat Maut sok-sokan pakai baju renang imut!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.50,0:17:16.86,Utama,Kitagawa,0,0,0,,Kau datang juga, ya, Kitagawa-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:18.71,Miring,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Acuhkan, acuhkan ....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.48,0:17:23.85,Utama,Kitagawa,0,0,0,,Malaikat Maut yang pakai baju renang imut itu melanggar kodrat, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.19,0:17:26.05,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Tuh, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.28,0:17:29.28,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Kitagawa-kun juga mengira keimutanmu \Nsampai melanggar kodrat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.58,0:17:31.43,Utama,Kitagawa,0,0,0,,Aku nyindir, cok!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.93,0:17:36.14,Miring,Nishimura,0,0,0,,"Kitagawa-kun juga"?{\i0}{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:41.23,Miring,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Apa berarti Takada-kun juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:45.57,Utama,Kitagawa,0,0,0,,Lagian, kau selalu menafsirkan semuanya terlalu positif!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:47.66,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,A-Apa maksudmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:48.63,Utama,Kitagawa,0,0,0,,Dengar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:50.09,Utama,Kitagawa,0,0,0,,Aku hanya nyindir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.41,0:17:53.43,Utama,Kitagawa,0,0,0,,Artinya Nishimura tidak cocok memakai baju renang itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.92,0:17:58.28,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Apa kau lebih suka baju renang\N sekolah, Kitagawa-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:18:00.64,Utama,Kitagawa,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau bisa menyimpulkannya begitu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:05.38,Utama,Kasahara,0,0,0,,Idih! Kitagawa suka sama cewek yang\N pakai baju renang sekolah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.38,0:18:06.91,Utama,Kurokawa,0,0,0,,Dasar mesum.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.91,0:18:09.62,Utama,Kitagawa,0,0,0,,Hei! Ka-Kalian cabul!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.62,0:18:13.05,Utama,Kitagawa,0,0,0,,Lagian, siapa juga yang tertarik dengan baju renang kalian!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.05,0:18:14.81,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Aku juga paham, Kitagawa-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.31,0:18:18.84,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Cewek yang pakai baju renang memang menggoda, ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:20.56,Utama,Kitagawa,0,0,0,,Hentikan, Takada!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:23.06,Utama,Kitagawa,0,0,0,,Jangan buat aku tambah dicap mesum!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.06,0:18:24.39,Utama,Tanaka,0,0,0,,Hentikan saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:26.85,Utama,Tanaka,0,0,0,,Tak ada gunanya berurusan dengannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.85,0:18:28.22,Utama,Kitagawa,0,0,0,,Sialan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:30.88,Utama,Kitagawa,0,0,0,,Ah, nyebelin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:32.58,Utama,Kitagawa,0,0,0,,Kau juga jangan ketawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.58,0:18:34.38,Utama,Tanaka,0,0,0,,Jangan lampiaskan padaku, dong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.03,0:18:36.39,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Mereka pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.46,0:18:40.22,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Hino-kun juga sudah datang!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.93,0:18:43.38,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Hei! Sebelah sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.38,0:18:47.28,Kilas M,Takada,0,0,0,,Cewek yang pakai baju renang memang menggoda, ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.17,0:18:50.79,Miring,Takada,0,0,0,,Apa yang dia maksud "menggoda" ....
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.43,0:18:53.66,Miring,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Tidak, pasti bukan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.66,0:18:56.09,Miring,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Aku cuma terlihat sok-sokan imut.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.91,0:18:58.29,Miring,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Aku malu ....
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.87,0:19:00.55,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Oh ya, Nishimura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.55,0:19:00.98,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:05.00,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Baju renang itu imut banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.00,0:19:06.33,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Cocok banget untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.87,0:19:15.33,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Aku lupa mengatakannya tadi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.16,0:19:19.92,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Te-Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.36,0:19:23.88,Utama,Hino,0,0,0,,Di luar ada yang jual ramune.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.88,0:19:26.08,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Wah, kau membelikannya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.08,0:19:27.22,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Terima kasih!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:28.93,Utama,Hino,0,0,0,,Ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.83,0:19:31.54,Utama,Hino,0,0,0,,Nih, Nishimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:33.61,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Eh? Untukku juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.78,0:19:36.14,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:41.21,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Hino-kun, apa kau memakai baju renang sekolah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.21,0:19:42.02,Utama,Hino,0,0,0,,Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.02,0:19:45.34,Utama,Hino,0,0,0,,Kukira kenorakannya ini lumayan keren.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.34,0:19:48.34,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Eh? Aku sudah beli baru, tahu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.11,0:20:04.29,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Nishimura-san, ayo main sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.36,0:20:10.97,Miring,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Syukurlah aku membeli baju renang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.45,0:21:51.59,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Ka-Kamu terlihat senang banget, Takada-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.59,0:21:53.65,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Pulang mampir-mampir itu asik!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.65,0:21:55.04,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Apalagi bareng Nishimura-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.54,0:21:57.03,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Ti-Tidak benar ....
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.37,0:21:59.95,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Kau selalu terlihat kalem, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.95,0:22:01.76,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Senyumanmu juga cantik!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.16,0:22:06.97,Kilas,Kurokawa,0,0,0,,Pasti serem kalau senyum.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.68,0:22:11.17,Kilas,Kitagawa,0,0,0,,Apa kalian tahu?\NSenyuman Malaikat Maut itu ....
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.44,0:22:16.75,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,A-Aku kurang suka dengan ekspresi senyumanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.75,0:22:18.73,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Oh, benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.98,0:22:23.20,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Kau memang tambah imut kalau tersenyum, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.69,0:22:24.73,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.06,0:22:27.85,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Padahal biasanya kau tampil kalem dan keren.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.85,0:22:30.66,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Tidak, tidak, tidak, kurasa kamu salah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.18,0:22:33.37,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Kau keren, kok, Nishimura-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.37,0:22:35.10,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Kan Malaikat Maut!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.72,0:22:39.41,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Ti-Tidak, bukan itu maksudku.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.85,0:22:46.50,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Aku ingin mengatakannya sejak dulu,\Naku terlihat seram dan tidak imut ....
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.50,0:22:49.13,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Biasanya kau tampil kalem banget, sih.{\i1}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.88,0:22:52.07,Miring,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Ka-Kalem banget?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.58,0:22:55.84,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Apa kau khawatir?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.84,0:23:00.06,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Apa kau takut sosok kalemmu akan \Nrusak kalau kau tersenyum?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.61,0:23:02.82,Miring,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Tidak, tidak pernah kepikiran, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.54,0:23:05.01,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Tenang saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.38,0:23:08.73,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Aku akan selalu berpihak padamu!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.49,0:23:15.07,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Bagaimanapun senyumanmu, \Naku tidak akan pernah membencimu!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.76,0:23:18.30,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Walau kau tidak kalem pun, aku tidak peduli!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.30,0:23:20.82,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Kau boleh tersenyum sebanyak-banykanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.28,0:23:24.79,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,I-Iya, terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.96,0:23:30.23,Utama,Nishimura,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.23,0:23:32.74,Utama,Takada,0,0,0,,Eh? Kenapa ngucapin dua kali?
